      "text": "WAL File                                                                                                                                      \n    |                                                                                                                                             \n    +----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+          \n    | WAL Block                                                                        |                                                      \n    |                                                                                  |                                                          \n    | +----------------+-------------------------------------------------------------+ |            \n    | | WalBlockHeader | BlockPayload                                                | |                                      \n    | +----------------+-------------------------------------------------------------+ |            \n    | |<---- 16 B ---->|<-------------------------- len ---------------------------->| |             \n    |                                                                                  |                                                          \n    |                  BlockPayload, no compression                                    |                                        \n    |                  |                                                               |                                                          \n    |                  +----------------+----------------+-------------+              |                                \n    |                  | WalRecord #0   | WalRecord #1   | Padding     |              |                                 \n    |                  +----------------+----------------+-------------+              |                                \n    |                                   |                |<padding_len>|              |                                                     \n    |                                                                                  |                                                          \n    |                  BlockPayload, compressed                                        |                                          \n    |                  |                                                               |                                                          \n    |                  +----------+-------------------------------+-------------+      |                         \n    |                  | raw_size | compressed WalRecords         | Padding     |      |                            \n    |                  +----------+-------------------------------+-------------+      |                         \n    |                  |<-- 4 B ->|<-------- compressed_len ------>|<padding_len>|      |                 \n    +----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "WAL File                                                                                                                                      \n    |                                                                                                                                             \n    +----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+                                                          \n    | WAL Block                                                                        |                                                          \n    |                                                                                  |                                                          \n    | +----------------+-------------------------------------------------------------+ |                                                          \n    | | WalBlockHeader | BlockPayload                                                | |                                                          \n    | +----------------+-------------------------------------------------------------+ |                                                          \n    | |<---- 16 B ---->|<-------------------------- len ---------------------------->| |                                                          \n    |                                                                                  |                                                          \n    |                  BlockPayload, no compression                                    |                                                          \n    |                  |                                                               |                                                          \n    |                  +----------------+----------------+-------------+              |                                                           \n    |                  | WalRecord #0   | WalRecord #1   | Padding     |              |                                                           \n    |                  +----------------+----------------+-------------+              |                                                           \n    |                                   |                |<padding_len>|              |                                                           \n    |                                                                                  |                                                          \n    |                  BlockPayload, compressed                                        |                                                          \n    |                  |                                                               |                                                          \n    |                  +----------+-------------------------------+-------------+      |                                                          \n    |                  | raw_size | compressed WalRecords         | Padding     |      |                                                          \n    |                  +----------+-------------------------------+-------------+      |                                                          \n    |                  |<-- 4 B ->|<-------- compressed_len ------>|<padding_len>|      |                                                         \n    +----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+",
      "autoResize": false,
