      "text": "    Wal Block Uncompressed\n    +----------------+-------------------------------------+-------------+                \n    | WalBlockHeader | WalRecord #0 ... WalRecord #N       | Padding     |                \n    +----------------+-------------------------------------+-------------+                \n    |<---- 16 B ---->|<----------- len - padding_len ----->|<padding_len>|                \n                     |<-------------------- len ------------------------>|",
